Frontiers | Explore the efficacy of microwave ablation combined with fruquintinib and tislelizumab in the treatment of metastatic colorectal cancer
===============

ORIGINAL RESEARCH article
-------------------------

Front. Oncol., 24 February 2026

Sec. Gastrointestinal Cancers: Colorectal Cancer

Volume 16 - 2026 | [https://doi.org/10.3389/fonc.2026.1728876](https://doi.org/10.3389/fonc.2026.1728876)

Explore the efficacy of microwave ablation combined with fruquintinib and tislelizumab in the treatment of metastatic colorectal cancer
=======================================================================================================================================

*   [![Image 1: Wei Qian ](https://loop.frontiersin.org/images/profile/3221890/74) Wei Qian †](https://loop.frontiersin.org/people/3221890)
